author: Lee Camp
title: Why The Mainstream Media Doesn't Want You To Know What Happened In Iceland
text:
Why The Mainstream Media Doesn't Want You To Know What Happened In Iceland Recently, Iceland has prosecuted and jailed three more bankers involved in the Icelandic financial crash of 2008. This is great news, but Lee asks, why aren’t we doing the same? Lee follows up with shocking facts surrounding the number of U.S. bankers arrested and who we are willing to go after.
